headline: Raymond James Recruits Another Big Ex-Commonwealth Team
summary: The firm’s latest recruits managed approximately $682 million in client assets at LPL Financial, which bought Commonwealth Financial Network last year.

headline: Meet Hazel, the AI Tool That Sparked a Stock Market Selloff
summary: Advisors using fintech Altruist’s AI-powered Hazel platform are bullish on the technology’s power to boost their business. “The hype is real,” says one advisor.
